  "subject": "Simplify the helm override file handling",
  "commit_message": "Simplify the helm override file handling\n\nThis is a followup for change 89022.\nIt simplifies things by not including the app helm override in the overrides\nlist directly. Instead it is always appended last\nby application-override role after it's generated at runtime.\nAlso the variable with overrides has a new name and is an empty list by\ndefault.\n\nChange-Id: Id7f448922905ecd6d4434db87058dd17b2f34d9c\nIssue-ID: OOM-1861\nSigned-off-by: Michal Zegan <m.zegan@samsung.com>\n",
